      "title": "Unique Corals Rainbow Hyacinthus",
      "handle": "unique-corals-rainbow-hyacinthus",
      "body_html": "<p><em><strong><span>This is a \"Frag to Order\" item.\u00a0 Sold as a single frag directly from our mother colonies.</span></strong></em></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><em><strong>What to expect?\u00a0</strong></em></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><em><strong><span>Our signature line of coral are farmed under our care in multiple tanks.</span></strong></em></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Besides getting little clones of our favorite corals, you can expect an email with an expected ship date for you to approve as well as a picture of the actual WYSIWYG frags you are going to receive.\u00a0 Housed in perfect conditions, inspected daily and cared for by coral lovers- that is the formula we use so shop with confidence.\u00a0\u00a0</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Shown is one of our mother colonies which frags are taken from.\u00a0 While sizing varies from piece to piece, rest assured that we are fully aware that everyone would love as big of a frag as possible.\u00a0 These are typically a minimum of 1\" when cut.\u00a0 We do aim to please!</p>",
